  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "「GetBackers奪還屋 〜地獄のスカラムーシュ〜」では、漫画「GetBackers Retrievers」のキャラクターを操作し、街で情報を集めて依頼されたアイテムを奪還します。仲間との相性によって、彼らの戦闘能力が変化します。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "GetBackers Dakkanya: Jigoku no Scaramouche is an Action game, published by Konami, which was released in Japan in 2001.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "You control a character from the comic \"GetBackers Retrievers\" to gather information in the city and retrieve the requested items. Depending on the compatibility of your companions, their abilities in battle will change.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
